  m_text: This is where Granny can receive hammer, jump, and status rounded glamours!
    These are upgrades that will make the gameplay expereince a little more fun,
    and will make earning a high score a lot easier. Once you get a glamour, you
    get to keep it forever! (unless you delete the save of course...) Take your time
    and have fun applying glamors!
